title: Paige Bueckers Stands to Earn More in College Than She Would As a Pro
description: UConn guard Paige Bueckers could jump to the W.N.B.A. when she recovers from her knee injury. But experts said she may be better off financially by staying in college.
dc:creator: Adam Zagoria
media:description: Paige Bueckers, playing in the N.C.A.A. women's basketball tournament in March, tore a knee ligament last month.
